まず最初にタイムリーに頭山ニュース<br />
<A CLASS="line" HREF="http://sports.nifty.com/headline/entertainment/20030215_4.htm" TARGET="_blank">http://sports.nifty.com/headline/entertainment/20030215_4.htm</A><br />
